co.lotc.core.agnostic

Class AbstractChatBuilder<E extends AbstractChatBuilder<E>>

  • java.lang.Object
    • co.lotc.core.agnostic.AbstractChatBuilder<E>
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    ChatBuilder, ChatBuilder

    public abstract class AbstractChatBuilder<E extends AbstractChatBuilder<E>>
extends java.lang.Object
    Wrapper class around ComponentBuilder with lots of syntactic sugar. Doesn't extend ComponentBuilder because it is final. Unfortunately this means we lose their javadoc on these methods
